Class
Description
account_Manager
Controller class to route to either student_account, staff_account or user_registration depending on user Menu provided by this class is the first line of interaction between user and the program.
Attendee
When the Camp Attendee user chooses an option from the menu, they will be directed to this class to complete the required functions.
Attendee_Account
When a Camp Attendee logs in, they will first see the menu provided by this class.
Camp
Camp class is to represent a camp.
campData
This class represents entity class campData to hold and process data of camps.
Committee
When the Camp committee member chooses an option from the menu, they will be directed to this class to complete the required functions.
Committee_Account
When a Camp committee member logs in, they will first see the menu provided by this class.
CommitteeGenerateReport
Functionality for a committee member to generate a CSV/txt report on Attendee List, and Committee List.
CSVDataManager
This class is a Controller class to load and update CSVs (data) of different classes such as Students, Attendees, Committee etc.
CSVWriter
Controller class to write new information for the first time to CSV (data) of several classes, such as Student User, Attendee, Committee, etc.
